    "client_msg_id": "E773484B-D1D2-4FD2-97D9-A3CE96D5B6D4",
    "text": "Hi,\n\nWe've now had 3 remote meetups at roughly the same time: 16:00 UTC.\nHowever, we want to do a short poll to gather some info on possible other time's to see if we can schedule our next meetup differently or even have multiple meetups on different times. \n\nSo, can you please respond with one (or more) responses from the below choices (2 questions):\n\n1. On what time would you attend a FoC meetup?\nA) 9:00 AWST/CST (+8 UTC)\nB) 13:00 AWST/CST \nC) 17:00 AWST/CST\nD) 21:00 AWST/CST\n\nE) 9:00 CET (+2 UTC)\nF) 13:00 CET\nG) 17:00 CET\nH) 21:00 CET\n\nI) 9:00 MST (-7 UTC)\nJ) 13:00 MST\nK) 17:00 MST\nL) 21:00 MST\n\n2. On what day of the week would you attend a FoC meetup? (weekends included)\n\nThanks for your help!",
    "team": "T5TCAFTA9",
    "thread_ts": "1721931158.072789",
