                "text": "A) 9:00 AWST/CST (+8 UTC)\nB) 13:00 AWST/CST \nC) 17:00 AWST/CST\nD) 21:00 AWST/CST\n\nE) 9:00 CET (+2 UTC)\nF) 13:00 CET\nG) 17:00 CET\nH) 21:00 CET\n\nI) 9:00 MST (-7 UTC)\nJ) 13:00 MST\nK) 17:00 MST\nL) 21:00 MST\n\n2. On what day of the week would you attend a FoC meetup? (weekends included)\n\nThanks for your help!"
